<br>
a) have fun - enjoying your time online as you choose to enjoy it<br>
b) get where we want to go<br>
c) loot - equip each member as they most desire to be equipped (You won't get everything you want, this is not Afterlife, but if there's something you want that the guild can get, you can expect to get it, or get a general upgrading of your loot)<br>
